                "invention-title": [
                    "Carbon material and hydrogen co-production device",
                    "一种碳材料和氢气联产装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a carbon material and hydrogen co-production device, and relates to the technical field of petroleum and natural gas chemical production, the carbon material and hydrogen co-production device comprises an energy supply unit, a cracking reaction unit and a carbon material storage transition unit which are arranged in sequence, the energy supply unit provides heat for the cracking reaction unit, the cracking reaction unit is filled with a catalytic medium, and the carbon material storage transition unit is filled with hydrogen. The catalytic medium is kept in a liquid state under the action of heat provided by the energy supply unit, a feed gas inlet structure is arranged at the bottom of the cracking reaction unit, a solid carbon material discharging structure is arranged on the upper middle portion of the cracking reaction unit, and the carbon material storage transition unit is hollow and forms a storage cavity. The storage cavity is connected with the solid carbon material discharging structure and stores the solid carbon material overflowing from the solid carbon material discharging structure. The carbon material and hydrogen co-production device provided by the invention catalyzes the cracking of hydrocarbon gas fuel based on a liquid medium to generate a high-value carbon material and hydrogen."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提出一种碳材料和氢气联产装置，涉及石油天然气化工生产技术领域，该碳材料和氢气联产装置包括顺序设置的供能单元、裂解反应单元和碳材料储存过渡单元，供能单元为裂解反应单元提供热量，裂解反应单元内填充有催化介质，催化介质在供能单元提供的热量的作用下保持为液态，裂解反应单元底部设有原料气进气结构，裂解反应单元中上部设有固体碳材料排出结构，碳材料储存过渡单元内部中空并形成有储存腔，储存腔与固体碳材料排出结构相连接并储存由固体碳材料排出结构溢出的固体碳材料。本发明提出的碳材料和氢气联产装置基于液态介质催化碳氢化合物气体燃料裂解生成高值碳材料以及氢气。"
                }
            ]
